border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        form button {\n            background-color: #800000; /* Rich Maroon */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        form button:hover {\n            background-color: #600000; /* Darker Maroon */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Historical Preservation Society</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#projects\">Our Projects</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section intro-section\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Our Society</h2>\n            <p>Dedicated to preserving the rich history and cultural heritage of our community for future generations.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Founded in [Year], the Historical Preservation Society strives to identify, protect, and promote the historical assets that define our region. We believe that understanding our past is crucial for shaping a vibrant future. Through research, advocacy, and community engagement, we work to ensure that our historical landmarks and stories are not forgotten.</p>\n            <p>Our members are passionate historians, architects, community leaders, and concerned citizens united by a common goal: to safeguard our heritage.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"projects\" class=\"projects-section\">\n            <h2>Our Projects</h2>\n            <div class=\"projects-grid\">\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Restoration of the Old Mill</h4>\n                    <p>Successfully restored the historic Old Mill, transforming it into a museum and community center.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Plaque Program</h4>\n                    <p>Initiated a program to place historical plaques on significant buildings, increasing public awareness.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Oral History Archive</h4>\n                    <p>Collecting and archiving oral histories from long-time residents to capture personal experiences of the past.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Advocacy for Historic Districts</h4>\n                    <p>Successfully advocated for the designation of two new historic districts to protect architectural integrity.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"gallery-section\">\n            <h2>Gallery</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery-grid\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/800000/ffffff?text=Historic+Site+1\" alt=\"Historic Site 1\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/800000/ffffff?text=Historic+Site+2\" alt=\"Historic Site 2\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/800000/ffffff?text=Historic+Site+3\" alt=\"Historic Site 3\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/800000/ffffff?text=Historic+Site+4\" alt=\"Historic Site 4\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/800000/ffffff?text=Historic+Site+5\" alt=\"Historic Site 5\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/800000/ffffff?text=Historic+Site+6\" alt=\"Historic Site 6\">\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have a question, a historical discovery to share, or interested 